{
  "text": "There exist multiple more complex solutions for applying CNNs to action recognition [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . Some of these solutions rely on optical flow [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] , which is slow to evaluate. Others rely on a recurrent architecture [CITATION_7] [CITATION_8] , which is often difficult to train in practice.",
  "correct_citation": {
